---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="No Script Youtube!">
  <main class="text-center mt-20 ml-36 mr-36">
    <div>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold">ðŸš« No Script YouTube</h1>
      <p class="mt-4">
        Welcome to NoScript Youtube! A youtube client that doesn't use
        javascript!
      </p>
    </div>
    <hr class="mt-5 mb-5" />
    <div>
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold">How it works?</h1>
      <p>
        For the video, the URL that matches the source of the video is taken and
        the HTML5 video player is used to display it. Instead, for other
        information, the
        <a
          href="https://www.npmjs.com/package/ytdl-core"
          class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">ytdl-core</a
        > library of nodejs is used, which through web scraping takes basic information
        such as channel and recommended videos. The styling uses <a
          href="https://tailwindcss.com/"
          class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">TailwindCSS</a
        >
      </p>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
